To implement data synchronization mechanisms between the portal and the core banking system reliably and timely, we will develop models, services, controllers, and routes to handle data synchronization. This will ensure that data fetched from or updated to the core banking system is always in sync with the portal.

Epic Title: Core Banking System Integration

We will create necessary files within the `backend/integration` directories: `models`, `services`, `controllers`, and `routes`.

